      "text": "いえ、気にしないで下さい。正直なところ、予想外\n過ぎて、私も少し慌ててしまいましたけど……っ……",
      "startTime": 241.9666564942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "……っ、あははっ、まさか{user}さんが\nあんなに子供みたいにはしゃぐなんて、あははっ",
      "startTime": 249.9333231609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依の挑戦を見ていたら、俺まで熱くなってしまってな\nそ、それだけの力が、この挑戦にはあったんだよ",
      "startTime": 264.1333231609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_02-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、ありがとうございます\n思いっきり笑って、すっきりしました",
      "startTime": 271.1333231609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
